                Mr. Ness Edwards
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9f58d3c6-19b7-42aa-b519-1cd1fb058f9d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
