        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-abfedfa3-5e7e-46a4-9ae1-9f0753bcea1e">
                Mr. Gerald Williams  (Tonbridge) (seated and covered)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-abfedfa3-5e7e-46a4-9ae1-9f0753bcea1e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-04-19/debates/98f02d30-a5b6-4b4c-9ed5-d9f018986a87/PostOfficeServices(IncreasedCharges)#contribution-abfedfa3-5e7e-46a4-9ae1-9f0753bcea1e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">On a point of order, Mr. Deputy-Chairman. I heard you call "Lock the doors" when the right hon. Gentleman the Minister of Works was in this Chamber and I have just seen him come out of the Lobby. Will you call another Division, or what are you prepared to do?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
