<p class="">It is a reasonable time. After four minutes after the second call I give the order "Lock the Doors," and the Messenger locks the doors as quickly as he can. It cannot be done at once, but it is done in a reasonable time.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
